title: Submissions WG Pilot 5
text:
Objectives
The objectives of the R Consortium R Submission Pilot 5 Project are:

Deliver a publicly accessible R-based Submission through the eCTD portal using datasetjson.
Expand on the work done in Submission Pilot 1 and Pilot 3, by now utilizing R to generate ADaM datasets.

title: JSON Viewer
text:
This JSON Viewer is a Shiny-based solution originally developed for the 3rd CDISC Dataset-JSON Viewer Hackathon for which it won an honorable mention. It allows you to interactively explore and analyze CDISC Dataset-JSON data. Credit goes to the original developers of the application. The repo for the app can be found here.
It is embedded below with the help of shinylive.io. The app should load below; otherwise, please click here.
